defaultD. defaultRights Advocacydefault. 
defaultEnabling Palestinian residents to access their legal and social rights is of utmost importance in paving the way for a 
defaultpeaceful future in the region. Two examples of important projects, initiated by the Jerusalem Foundation together with its partners, are the  
defaultAtta’a Assistance Centre for the Rights of East Jerusalem Residents
default and 
defaultGrey Action (Council for the Rights of the
default Elderly).
